---

## If it DOES NOT exist — create it

Create a new file at exactly this path:
```
client/public/manifest.json
```
And paste the JSON above into it.

---

## Your `client/public/` folder should look like this:
```
client/public/
├── index.html       ✅ already have this
├── manifest.json    ✅ create or update this
├── _redirects       ✅ create this (fixes Netlify 404)
├── robots.txt       ✅ optional
└── favicon.ico      ✅ optional (React default)
